{"tid":1720701,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"戴妖有嘢講！激盪人心！","createTime":"2019-11-14T12:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T12:35:56.000Z","uid":268196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"784d771b34ac6b4ce8919b45ee0bc9de334b6a2c","tid":1720701,"uid":268196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:30:02.000Z","msg":"闊別五年，大家卒之重回佔領了！俾啲掌聲自己！<br />\n<br />\n係唔係想咁？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n覺唔覺得我哋而家同2014係咪有啲野好似？<br />\n<br />\n我係經歷過2014的廢老，廢噏之前，我先表示不割蓆、不分化！但有少少嘢想提一提：<br />\n<br />\n五個月嚟，我哋最厲害嘅，係流水戰略，有進有退，退完又進，你估我唔到。但中大守戰過後，浪漫陣地感覺重現，傘運味又漸濃。有人提出要堅守中大及各大學，結果出現幾個熟悉的情景：<br />\n<br />\n一）手足死守陣地<br />\n二）物資湧去某地點<br />\n三）快樂陣地片段重現<br />\n四）政府突然任你守陣地、任你佔路，讓市民持續感到不便，然後等民意慢慢散<br />\n<br />\n最後會點？等到大家悲壯地守到謝晒、民意弱晒，然後放狗入嚟收你皮，運動完結。 <br />\n<br />\n係唔係想重蹈覆轍？<br />\n<br />\nSorry, 可能語氣重咗，但真心想提。<br />\n不割蓆！不分化！不放棄！唔完美，可接受，可改善。"},{"pid":"f6d216e8c879f3480f6515f3fbd7f78f114c08ff","tid":1720701,"uid":15605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c249e00df6e1207c49138c53e132cd5dccfd6e38","tid":1720701,"uid":331879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:33:08.000Z","msg":"咁有咩suggestions<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51fd67c924e6967dec1ec93929baf931a52d3e4","tid":1720701,"uid":21193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:33:19.000Z","msg":"值得思考"},{"pid":"de1fa456af8443e13b6811e691e6d89e6e25531e","tid":1720701,"uid":268196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:35:21.000Z","msg":"自推十野"},{"pid":"13e9dff07b2e92e4b9f0ad106830843ca872d841","tid":1720701,"uid":268196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:35:34.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c7146c528439c759606845ebb37e30b27a046a30","tid":1720701,"uid":268196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2acccef2735bafdbcfcb4100382b6377d06d569d","tid":1720701,"uid":268196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T12:35:56.000Z","msg":"再推"}]}